{"tid":1717202,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"向警員高呼「照夠未」　屯門男被捕","createTime":"2019-11-13T14:15:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T15:16:06.000Z","uid":156878,"like":17,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1b32ba0655783492cd190a9649888de32868ae9e","tid":1717202,"uid":156878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:15:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/429928204384503/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F429928204384503%2F&d=jGmFyvXa%2BxCeqK61Wy4eywmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=1445f140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/429928204384503/</a><br />\n<br />\n10 萬次觀看 &middot; 星期一 &middot; <br />\n屯門鄉事會路及杯渡路一帶在11日晚上約有百多名人士堵路，並起火焚燒障礙物。大批防暴警察及後到場驅散，曾舉起黑旗、橙旗等作警告，施放多枚催淚彈驅散聚集人士。其後少量聚集人士退至河傍街一帶，防暴警察從多處包抄，其中有五名人士在青賢街的停車場被捕，及有一名男子在鄉事會路被捕。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有一名男子路過時被警察用電筒照射，該名男子向警方大叫「照夠未呀」，多名警員隨即跑至對面馬路並將該名男子制服，及立即以索帶綁起雙手作拘捕。"},{"pid":"4538316c346e3dc6b0773dd258f1d30362f371ed","tid":1717202,"uid":156878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c29d8d139e6dda91d5ca212192efefc2fb635ef7","tid":1717202,"uid":134116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:20:00.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"805b26296eedbaf40e2203e5738f29711a3e706b","tid":1717202,"uid":156878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad99576846ceca9210c7617b36dd781b8916a03e","tid":1717202,"uid":40010,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:21:54.000Z","msg":"真係狗嚟，主人一叫就跑哂上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi